race.description: Bunbury Cup On Sale Now Handicap (C1)
race.comment: WILUNA LASS (7) was too strong two starts back when clearing her maiden status at Ascot, and then had a genuine excuse last time out when finishing seventh over 1000m in a far stronger field than this. She is perfectly placed with a 2kg claim and can bounce back to take this out. ALEBRIJE (8) jumped from the inside draw to take up the running last start and fought hard for a comfortable win over 1100m at this track by just over a length. She benefits from a 3kg claim and will take some pegging back again. RIPPER FAROOQ (1) resumes after six months, having finished fifth over 1200m at Ascot first-up last prep. He is now with new trainers Chris & Michael Gangemi and will be fitter for a recent quiet trial at Lark Hill. Include. PINGERS (6) comes to hand quickly, so include in all combos.
